```{.r .cell-code}
#filter to only species of interest - takes it from 94632 obs to 21425 vars
scallops <- svcat %>% 
  filter(SCIENTIFIC_NAME=="Placopecten magellanicus (sea scallop)" | 
           SCIENTIFIC_NAME =="Placopecten magellanicus (sea scallop clapper)")

scallops <- scallops %>% 
  mutate(name = as.factor(SCIENTIFIC_NAME),
         cruise6 = as.factor(CRUISE6),
         cruise = as.factor(CRUISE),
         .keep = "unused")

summary(scallops)
```
